  Teng-hu5 so2 thiaN kau3 chia koh khui-siaN hau2, siuN7 kong2 kin-a2-jit8 i thai3 e7 hou7 Mou5-kui2 jip8-sim, cho3 kau3 chiah-nih thang kiaN e5 su7. Sian-siN-niu5 in bo2, kiaN2 khoaN3 chit e5 cheng5-heng5 ia7 si7 chin kan-khou2, chiu7 koh chit8 pai2 tai7-ke saN-chio kui7-loh8 lai5 ui7-tioh8 Teng-hu5 so2 jin7-choe7, Teng- hu5 so2 ia7 kui7-loh8 ka-ti7 jin7 kui2-ku3 choe7 ti7 Siong7-te3 e5 bin7-cheng5. I chi2-u7 siuN7 i un2-tang3 e7 hou7 cheng3-hu2 liah8-khi3, chit8-si5 siuN7 kong2 kin-a2-jit8 i thai5 e7 cho3 kau3 chiah kian3-siau3, m7-na7 hian7-chai7 tiong7-hu e5 ka- teng5 e5 the2-bian7, kap au7-thau5 e5 pe7-bo2 e5 bin7-phoe5, koh phah-sng2 i thak8 hiah che7 chheh. Kin-a2-jit8 na7 it-tan3 khia7 ti7 hoat- teng5 lai5 siu7 kong-phoaN3, cheng3-lang5 teh khoaN3, lai5 siu7 sat-hu e5 si2-heng5 phoaN3-koat, hit-si5 i beh thai2 u7 bin7 thang kiN3 lang5. Chit8-si5 kiaN kau3 ngiauh8-ngiauh8-chhoah, koh-khah hau2. Hau2 kau3 bak8-chiu ham-ham, phiN7-chui2 khok8-khok8-tin. 
  Na7-si7 sian-siN-niu5 in khoaN3 i an2-ni, soa3 siuN7 bo5 sim2-mih8 oe7 thang an-ui3 i, ia7 si7 kap i thin7-thau5 hau2, koh chit8 pai2 chhim- chhim kam2-kak choe7 e5 li7-hai7. Sian-siN- niu5 koh the3 i ki5-to2, chai chi2-u7 ki5-to2 kiu5 Chu2 seng3 chhiu2 giah8 koan5, i2-goa7 bo5 lou7. 
  Au7-lai5 an-ui3--i, ka7 i kong2, ng3-bang7 Teng-hu5 hiaN bo5 kau3 si2 e5 te7-pou7, ng3-bang7 Chu2 in-tian2 lin2, e7 koh u7 chit8 pai2 thoan5-oan5 e5 ki-hoe7. An-ui3 soah, jit8 i2-keng mng2-pou, Teng-hu5 so2 chiu7 ka-ti7 koat-sim, bo5-lun7 chaiN2-iuN7 bo5 to3-khi3 chit8 choa7 ia7 si7 be7 eng7-tit, chiu7 koat-i3 beh to3-khi3. 
  Sian-siN-niu5 in bo2-kiaN2 chiu7 sang3 i khi3 kau3 theng5-chhia-tiuN5, ia7 chiong chit8 pun2 Seng3-keng sang3--i, soa3 chhiaN2 i siong5 thak8 Seng3-keng, ki5-to2. Teng-hu5 so2 chiu7 che7 chhia to3-khi3. 
  Chiah kong2 Teng-hu5 hiaN hou7 lang5 siat-hoat khi3 i-iN7. Sui-jian5 m7-si7 chin tang7 siong, iau2-ku2 tioh8 chiaN5-chap8 jit8 e5 ti7-liau5 chiah e7 ho2. Ui7 se3-kan-thai3 (世間態) kiaN-liau2 phaiN2-khoaN3-siuN3, koh ka- ti7 e5 te7-ui7, bin7-phoe5 e5 koan-he7, koh bo5 ti3- kau3 si2 e5 siong, chiu7 bo5 khi3 po3 keng2-chhat. Ia7 jip8-iN7 khah be7 hou7 lang5 lai5 bian7- hoe7, kou5-ioh8 ia7 khah li7-pian7, chu7 an2-ni bih tiam3 i-iN7 ti7-liau5, sia2 bian7-hoe7 sia7- choat8 e5 toaN tah ti7 goa7-bin7. Oan5-che2 khoaN3 se3-bin7 an2-ni ia7 chin kho2-lin5 in, cheng5-jit8 hou7 in siak iam5-bi2 e5 su7 long2 bo5 koh ki3 ti7 sim, chhu3-piN tai7 koe3-khi3 lai7- bin7 ka7 i khioh-khioh ho2-se3, chong2-phou e5 hoeh ka7 i chhit-chhit leh, mng5 chhoe7 chit8 mng5 so2 ka7 i so2 leh, ia7 chiong hit e5 7 hoe3 e5 cha-bou2 gin2-na2 ka7 i chhoa7 khi3 chhu3-nih. Ia7 khi3 ka7 Teng-hu5 hiaN kong2 i u7 the3 i siat-hoat lai7-bin7, koh gin2- na2 chhoa7 khi3 ti7 i hia, Teng-hu5 hiaN peng5- seng chai Oan2-che2 in chit8 ke si7 pai3 Siong7-te3. Ia7 tak8 hang7 chin gau5-cho3, chin u7 thiaN3-sim, chiu7 chin seh-sia7. 
  Kong2 Teng-hu5 so2 che7 chiuN7 hoe2-chhia, sim chin hoan5-lo2, long2 m7-kaN2 giah8-thau5 khi2-lai5 khoaN3 lang5, chi2-u7 sim-lai7 am3-am3 ki5-to2. Kong2, Siong7-te3 ah ! Ia5-sou Kiu3- chu2 ah ! Li2 na7-si7 u7-iaN2, u7 leng5, u7 siaN3, Li2 tioh8 kiu3 goa2 chit8 tiau5 kau2 mia7. Goa2 to7-si7 m7-bat chiah e7 cho3 kau3 chit ho7 choe7. Li2 na7 su3 goa2 peng5-an, Ia5-sou li2 na7 the3 goa2 taN chit e5 taN3, goa2 chian7-pi7 tek-khak goan7 cho3 li2 e5 lou5-chai5, cha-bou2-kan2, goan7 po3 li2 e5 in, si3-ke3 lai5-khi3 kong2 li2 e5 to7 hou7 lang5 thiaN. Sim-te2 chit8 ku3 ia7 goa2 Ia5-sou li2 tioh8 cho3 goa2 e5 Chu2, li2 e5 chhiu2 tioh8 giah8-koan5, jiau5 goa2 chian7-pi7 chit8 tiau5 kau2-mia7. Nng7-ku3 ia7 goa2 Chu2 Ia5-sou li2 tioh8 cho3 goa2 e5 Chu2, jiau5 goa2 chian7-pi7 kau2- mia7. Cheng5-jit8 e5 phui2-phui2 Ia5-sou phui2- phui2, long2 be7 ki3-tit lah. Bak8-sai2 sip-sip lau5, chhiu2-kin na2 chhit, bian2 loa7-ku2 chiu7 kau3 ui7 loh8 chhia, kio3 chit8 tiuN jin5-lek8- chhia chit khun3 piaN3 kau3 in chhu3. 
  Kau3-ui7 khoaN3-kiN3 mng5 so2 leh, sim-koaN chhiak8 chit8--e7, siuN7 kong2 taN hai7 lah, tai7- khai3 si7 chong3-sek liau2 lah. Ia7 gin2-na2 tai7-khai3 si7 siu7 cheng3-hu2 po2-hou7, chiong- lai5 ti7 hoat-teng5 thang cho3 i5-it e5 cheng3- jin5. In-ui7 teh thai5 hoah kiu3-lang5 e5 si5, lai7-bin7 chi2-u7 chit e5 gin2-na2 ti7-teh na7-tiaN7. Tu2 teh kiaN e5 si5, Oan5-che2 tui3 keh-piah khoaN3-kiN3 chit8 e5 cha-bou2-lang5 che7 jin5- lek8-chhia, ia7 jit8 i2-keng beh am3, hoan2-ou lah, chhia-phang5 kham3-kham3 leh, m7-ai3 lang5 khoaN3. Tau3-ti2 chit e5 si7 sim2-mih8 lang5, chit8-e7 khoaN3 to7-si7 Teng-hu5 so2. Oan5-che2 koaN2-kin2 ka7 i kio3 jip8-khi3, gin2-na2 ia7 lai5 chhoe7 in lau7-bo2, Oan5-che2 chiah chiong chiah e5 su7 cheng5-thau5 it-li2 kong2 hou7 i thiaN. 
  Kong2 Teng-hu5 hiaN e5 siong bo5 loa7 tang7, i-seng kong2 oa2 chiaN5-chap8 jit8 chiu7 e7 ho2, hian7-chai7 jip8-iN7 tiong. Teng-hu5- so2 sim-koaN hoang3 chit8-e7, sim khui-khui khi3. Put-ti put-kak kong2 chit8 ku3, ah ! Kam2-sia7 Siong7-te3, Kiu3-chu2 Ia5-sou li2 u7 kiu3 goa2 chian7-pi7. 
  Oan5-che2 chin ki5-koai3, chit e5 peng5-si5 to7-si7 phui2-phui2 Ia5-sou e5 lang5, kin-a2-jit8 na2 e7 kong2 Siong7-te3 oe7, chin ki5-koai3 ! Oan5-che2 kin2 mng7 Teng-hu5 so2, li2 thai2 e7 kong2 kam2-sia7 Siong7-te3 ? Teng-hu5 so2 chiah chiong i kin-a2-jit8 beh khi3 Ko-bi2 thiau3 hai2, kau3 Chheng-chui2 sou2 tu2-tioh8 e5 su7. Ia7 chiah thau2 i e5 chhiu2-kin, chiong Seng3-keng hou7 Oan5-che2 khoaN3. Ah ! Oan5-che2 hoaN-hi2 kau3 lau5 bak8 sai2, nng7- lang5 chiah koh kui7-loh8 kam2-sia7 Chu2. Teng-hu5 so2 ia7 chai Teng-hu5 hiaN ui7 kiaN- liau2 ka-ti7 e5 te7-ui7 tui3 sia7-hoe7 phaiN2 khoaN3, koh bo5 kau3 loa7 tang7-siong, sou2-i2 bo5 khi3 po3 keng2-chhat. Su7 i3-goa7 e5 an-cheng7 bo5 tong7-iau5, sou2-i2 Teng-hu5 so2 koh chit8 hoan e5 chhim-chhim kam2-sia7 Siong7-te3. 
  Hit am3 Oan5-che2 lau5 Teng-hu5 so2 ti7 i e5 tau chiah8-png7, Teng-hu5 hiaN ti7 peN7-chhng5 kui2 hun ia7 si7 siuN7-tioh8 ka-ti7 e5 chho3, chiah e7 lai5 pek hu7-jin5-lang5 kiaN5 kau3 chit tiau5 lou7. Ia7 teh hoan5-lo2 ban7-it Teng-hu5 so2 na7 khi3 chu7-sat, i ia7 si7 chin toa7 e5 chek- seng5. Koh kam2-kek Oan5-che2 chit8 ke cho3 chhu3-piN, si7 pai3 Siong7-te3 lang5, chin chhin-chhiat. Sou2-i2 sim am3-am3 ia7 teh siuN7 kong2 chhu2-khi3 na7 e7 tit chit8 ke peng5- ho5, ia7 chin ai3 hou7 hu7-jin5-lang5 khi3 sin3-kau3. 
  Kong2 kau3 hit am3 Oan5-che2 chiu7 chio Teng-hu5 so2 khi3 i-iN7 khoaN3 Teng-hu5 hiaN. Teng-hu5 so2 khi2-thau5 m7-kaN2 khi3. Na7-si7 i tit8-tit8 ka7 i khou2-khng3. TaN li2 to ia7 beh jin7 Ia5-sou cho3 Chu2 lah, ban7-su7 tek-khak tioh8 lun2-khi3, eng7 ho2 iaN5 phai2, li2 sia3-bian2 lang5, Chu2 ia7 chiah beh sia3-bian2 li2. Khou2- khng3 liau2 Teng-hu5 so2 chiu7 kap Oan5-che2 cho3-hoe2 khi3. Chong2-si7 Oan5-che2 m7-kaN2 hou7 Teng-hu5-hiaN chai in Teng-hu5 so2 u7 beh kap i sin3 Ia5-sou, Teng-hu5 so2 ia7 m7-kaN2 kong2, in-ui7 kiaN-liau2 Teng-hu5 hiaN siu7- khi3, put-ko3 khi3 chhoe7--i, kap i hoe7 bin7. Tai7-ke ia7 bo5 oe7, i ia7 m7 seng khui-chhui3, i ia7 m7-goan7 seng khui-chhui3, chi2-u7 Oan5- che2 na2 ke-po5-leh, cho3-ho2 cho3-khiap kong2 kui2 ku3 oe7 chiu7 saN-si5 to3-khi3, Teng-hu5 so2 ia7 to3-khi3. 
  Hit am3 Teng-hu5 so2 ti7 Oan5-che2 in tau keh-me5, tai7-ke cho3-hoe2 cho3 ka-teng5 le2- pai3, thak8 Ma2-thai3, Ia5-sou kong2, Lang5 tioh8 thiaN3 tui3-tek8, koh le2-me7 lin2 e5 tioh8 the3 in chiok-hok, oan3-hin7 lin2 e5 tioh8 the3 i ki5-to2, Teng-hu5 so2 toa7 siu7 kam2-kek, keh bin5-a2 cha2-khi2 ka-ti7 chiu7 khi3 chhoe7 Teng-hu5-hiaN. 
  Teng-hu5 hiaN khoaN3 i toaN-sin lai5, chhiak8 chit8-e7, an3-sng3 cha-hng kap Oan5- che2 lai5 m7-kaN2, cha-khi2 ka-ti7 lai5, chit kioh chhiah cha-bou2 tek-khak si7 beh lai5 kap i toa7 nau7 chit8-leh lah. Sou2-i2 i ia7 chiu7 taN2-pan7 ho2-ho2, bin7 kek kau3 phong3 sai-sai, chhau3 kia5-kia5. Bo5 phah-sng3, oa2- lai5 koh khin-siaN se3-soeh, koh bak8-sai2 kam5 bak8-kiN5, chin u7 le2-sou3, thim3-thau5, chhim-chhim hoe7 i e5 m7-tioh8, chin kho2- ai3, chin sun5-cheng5 e5 khoan2-sit, cheng7- cheng7 khia7, chhiu2 theh8 chhiu2-kin-na2 ng ti7 bin7-nih, chhngh8-chhngh8-hau2, khin- siaN kong2, “Hu-kun chhiaN2 li2 sia3-bian2 goa2 e5 m7-tioh8, kiu5 li2 chiau3-ku7 thiaN3 goa2.” Ah ! Kah m7-si7 khim5-siu3 e5 Teng-hu5 hiaN na2 jim2-tit thiaN ka-ti7 e5 chhe-chu2 eng7 sun5-cheng5 kho2-ai3, hoan2-hoe2 e5 thai3-tou7 lai5 kong2 an-ui3 e5 oe7 leh. Chit8-si5 tong3 be7 tiau5, khoaN3 peN7-sek bo5 pat8 lang5 ti7- hia, chi2-u7 in nng7 hu-hu7 na7-tiaN7. Chu7 an2-ni peh khi2-lai5 che7 ti7 thih-bin5-chhng5-kiN, chhun-chhiu2 khan Teng-hu5 so2 kong2, 
  “Goa2, ai3-kheng li2 ia7-tioh8 sia3-bian2 goa2.” Nng7 e5 tiam3 hia tiap-a2-ku2 lau5 bak8-sai2, bo5 chit8 ku3 oe7 thang kong2. 
